                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970531-6-off21 t17970531-6-cd22"></join>, a cloth coar, value 2s. a pair of cloth breeches, value 12d. and a man's hat, value 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17970531-6-victim106" type="victimName">
